room_title: Escape room "Ex Machina" by Med City Escape in Rochester (MN)
review: This was my first escape room and we chose the middle difficulty room (Ex Machina). It was so much fun! I will definitely do more escape rooms and Med City was great! Their puzzle was challenging and fun!

room_title: Escape room "Ex Machina" by Med City Escape in Rochester (MN)
review: Really fun! I went with one person and we almost finished the Ex Machina room! It was fun and challenging. Definitely want to try the other rooms.
